      "message": "[🔴 Critical Issues - Must fix before merge] Line 65: `isPluginOverwrite: Body !\u003d\u003d OriginalBody` can mark ordinary messages as extension-modified if `OriginalBody` is empty, unset, or otherwise unavailable for messages that were never modified by a plugin. That would show the plugin indicator and original-message toggle incorrectly. Please gate this on OriginalBody being present and intentionally different from Body, or on an explicit backend-provided flag if available.\n```suggestion\nproperty bool isPluginOverwrite: OriginalBody !\u003d\u003d \"\" \u0026\u0026 Body !\u003d\u003d OriginalBody\n```",
